strings:
<voice_0x0100102F><se_low>King Trode: Well done, everyone! I'm at a loss as to how
we will proceed from here. But for tonight,
we must rest.

<voice_0x01001030><se_low>King Trode: I will spend the night in the wagon.
I don't want the Princess to be lonely.
Sleep well!
<voice_0x01001031><se_low>Yangus: Guv! Guv! This ain't good, guv!

<voice_0x01001032><se_low>Yangus: It's Jessica! She ain't nowhere around!
When I woke up, 'er bed was empty an'
all 'er stuff 'ad gone!
